definition: surname Yin/abbr. for 印度[Yin4 du4]
to print/to mark/to engrave/a seal/a print/a stamp/a mark/a trace/image

sentences.english: Witness Chengjiang People's Struggle Course And Happiness Marks.
sentences.chinese: 見證澄江人奮鬥歷程和幸福印跡。

sentences.english: If your entire foot is visible in the footprint, you have a flat foot.
sentences.chinese: 如果在印跡上雙腳清晰可見，那麼你就是平足。

sentences.english: Objective To perfect gene profile expressed in pre-implantation embryos.
sentences.chinese: 目的完善印跡基因在人類種植前胚胎的表達圖譜。

sentences.english: I can not wash out the marks from the shirt.
sentences.chinese: 我難以從襯衫上洗去印跡。

sentences.english: An improved immunoblotting method has been developed for the determination of apolipoprotein E, phenotypes.
sentences.chinese: 介紹一種免疫印跡法測定載脂蛋白E表型。

sentences.english: Bullets fired from a gun have striae based on the barrel used;
sentences.chinese: 在槍裏射出的子彈帶有槍管留下的條狀印跡。

sentences.english: Western blot showed the good immunological specificity of the IgY.
sentences.chinese: 經免疫印跡分析，具有良好的免疫學特異性。

sentences.english: Glossy colors, dried soon, could be mixed with photosensitive ink of all brands.
sentences.chinese: 顏色豔麗，印跡快乾，能與進口各品牌光敏印油混用。

sentences.english: It seems vaguely there was a red mark in Lily's neck.
sentences.chinese: 好像莉莉的脖頸間隱隱地真有一條紅色的印跡。

sentences.english: Western-blotting was used to observe the immune cross reactions.
sentences.chinese: 應用蛋白印跡觀察其與相關細菌的免疫交叉反應。

sentences.english: Objective To investigate whether genomic imprinting is involved in the etiology of tic disorder.
sentences.chinese: 目的研究遺傳印跡是否與抽動障礙的遺傳病因學有關。

sentences.english: We might find pick marks higher in the pin chambers, too.
sentences.chinese: 在珠孔的更高處，我們也可能找到印跡。

sentences.english: The content of heat shock protein 72 (HSP72) in cardiac muscle was measured by dot blot analysis.
sentences.chinese: 斑點印跡法測定心肌熱休克蛋白72含量。

sentences.english: Cell lysates were collected for Western blot analysis.
sentences.chinese: 收集到的細胞溶解液均進行免疫印跡分析。

sentences.english: The footprints blown off by the wind of Talimakan.
sentences.chinese: 塔克拉瑪干的風捲走了太多的印跡。

sentences.english: Sandwich ELISA, dot blotting and DNA sequencing methods were used for the identification of positive clones.
sentences.chinese: 通過硝酸纖維膜斑點印跡法進行陽性克隆鑑定。
